      <title>Slim 3筆記(1)安裝</title>
      <link href="/2018/09/14/Slim3%E7%AD%86%E8%A8%98(1)%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D/"/>
      <url>/2018/09/14/Slim3%E7%AD%86%E8%A8%98(1)%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%9D/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://discoversdkcdn.azureedge.net/postscontent/products/slim.png" alt="Slim3"><br><a id="more"></a></p><h1 id="為什麼要使用Slim-3"><a href="#為什麼要使用Slim-3" class="headerlink" title="為什麼要使用Slim 3"></a>為什麼要使用Slim 3</h1><h2 id="優點"><a href="#優點" class="headerlink" title="優點"></a>優點</h2><ul><li>和Laravel比較檔案較小</li><li>對主機要求較低，一般shared hosting也可以使用</li><li>模板可使用twig，也支援Eloquent</li><li>較簡約</li></ul><h2 id="缺點"><a href="#缺點" class="headerlink" title="缺點"></a>缺點</h2><ul><li>須有一定php基礎</li><li>不像Laravel那樣能夠快速上手</li></ul><h1 id="簡單開始"><a href="#簡單開始" class="headerlink" title="簡單開始"></a>簡單開始</h1><h2 id="使用-composer安裝"><a href="#使用-composer安裝" class="headerlink" title="使用 composer安裝"></a>使用 composer安裝</h2><pre><code>composer require slim/slim &quot;^3.0&quot;</code></pre><h2 id="建立-public-index-php"><a href="#建立-public-index-php" class="headerlink" title="建立/public/index.php"></a>建立/public/index.php</h2><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">require</span> <span class="keyword">__DIR__</span> . <span class="string">'/../bootstrap/app.php'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">$app-&gt;run();</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="建立-bootstrap-app-php"><a href="#建立-bootstrap-app-php" class="headerlink" title="建立/bootstrap/app.php"></a>建立/bootstrap/app.php</h2><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">session_start();</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">require</span> <span class="keyword">__DIR__</span> . <span class="string">'/../vendor/autoload.php'</span>;</span><br><span class="line">$app = <span class="keyword">new</span> \Slim\App([</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">'settings'</span> =&gt; [</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">'displayErrorDetails'</span> =&gt; <span class="keyword">true</span>, <span class="comment">//顯示錯誤</span></span><br><span class="line">    ],</span><br><span class="line">]);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">require</span> <span class="keyword">__DIR__</span> . <span class="string">'/../app/routes.php'</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="建立-app-routes-php"><a href="#建立-app-routes-php" class="headerlink" title="建立 /app/routes.php"></a>建立 /app/routes.php</h2><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$app-&gt;get(<span class="string">'/'</span>, <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="params">($request, $response)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="string">"Hello world"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="建立-public-htaccess"><a href="#建立-public-htaccess" class="headerlink" title="建立 public/.htaccess"></a>建立 public/.htaccess</h2><pre><code>RewriteEngine OnRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-fRewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-dRewriteRule ^ index.php [QSA,L]</code></pre><h2 id="開啟網頁"><a href="#開啟網頁" class="headerlink" title="開啟網頁"></a>開啟網頁</h2><p><a href="http://localhost/YourAppName/public" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://localhost/YourAppName/public</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
